                     <interp inst="t18210606-151-person1583" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Gosling, a <rs id="t18210606-151-viclabel875" type="occupation">pawnbroker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-151-victim1581 t18210606-151-viclabel875"></join>, the boots hung inside the door; the prisoner was stopped with them.</p>
               <p>(Property produced, and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded the utmost distress.</p>
               <p>
